    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In Medieval manuscripts and early printed books, small letters placed in spaces left blank for initials, to guide the illuminator or rubricator.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
